aterials, win epic bossfights and many, many more things to do. The sky is the limit. Literally.',0,'Role-playing (RPG), Simulator, Adventure, Indie',0,'//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/co5k66.jpg'),(195243,'Yummy Girl 2','Apr 08, 2022','Sweet buns, ruddy cupcakes, juicy burgers - all these yummy girls love to eat. They are just waiting for you to feed them! ( ˘▽˘)っ♨',0,'Indie',0,'//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/co59f3.jpg'),(197231,'Rhom Bus','Feb 22, 2017','New, addictive and clever game mechanics in a beautiful and carefully designed world of rhombuses. Turn the tiles or turn the board to complete the levels and help the animals getting on the bus.',0,'Puzzle',0,''),(197609,'Ys VIII: Lacrimosa of Dana - Deluxe Edition','Nov 15, 2022, Nov 18, 2022, Nov 25, 2022','Deluxe Edition Includes:\n\n- Ys VIII: Lacrimosa Of Dana PS5 Game\n- Mini Art Collection\n- Ys VIII: Lacrimosa of Dan, Select Soundtrack',0,'Role-playing (RPG), Adventure',0,'//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/co4ox0.jpg'),(202668,'Tom\'s Adventure','May 30, 2022','A little but very fun and challenging platform game.',0,'Adventure, Indie',0,'//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/co5nk2.jpg'),(203546,'Meat & Greed','Jun 07, 2022','In the atmospheric puzzle-platformer Meat & Greed, you will experience the horrors of a slaughterhouse from the perspective of different animals. Solve riddles and collaborate with other animals to try and escape this ill-fated factory.',0,'Adventure, Indie',0,'//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/co5kvy.jpg'),(209901,'Hidden Secrets: The Nightmare','Nov 19, 2008','',0,'',0,'//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/co4zmz.jpg'),(209902,'Hidden Stroke: APRM','May 29, 2003','',0,'',0,'//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/co4zn1.jpg'),(210938,'Phoenix Point: Complete Edition','','Phoenix Point: Complete Edition, the acclaimed strategy game from the creator of X-COM, is now assembled into the ultimate collection, including all DLCs, content updates, and product improvements over four years of development.',0,'Role-playing (RPG), Strategy, Tactical',0,'//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/co50tq.jpg'),(213046,'The Ultimate FMV Bundle 2','Aug 08, 2022','Wales Interactive is proud to offer the ultimate bundle for their very best FMV games! Featuring Night Book, Who Pressed Mute on Uncle Marcus? Bloodshore, Five Dates and I Saw Black Clouds in one bundle!',0,'',0,'//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/co52iy.jpg'),(230654,'Hockey de Mesa','Aug 2008','',0,'',0,''),(230918,'King\'s Hand: Seasonal Winter Pack','','A snowy reskin of the whole game.',0,'Sport, Strategy',0,''),(230919,'King\'s Hand: Exotic Purgatory Pack','','An exclusive hellish reskin of the whole game.',0,'Sport, Strategy',0,''),(232243,'Pixel Race: Endless Retro Racing','','Pixel Race is an endless racing game which you earn badges, unlock and\nupgrade cars while trying to win the Legendary badge.\n4 CARS\nEach new car is smaller and stronger than previous one!',0,'Racing, Sport',0,''),(232258,'Jello Bubbles: Pop Color Balls','','Play the new fun and addictive Jello Bubbles shooter game for FREE. Enjoy solving original bubble puzzles and relax popping colorful jelly balls.\nMatch 3 or more bubbles with the same color and clear levels, accomplish the game objective to advance to the next one.\nAim & shoot with the Jell-O-Matic Machine, to drop & blast all bubbles. A funny hummingbird helps you with nice boosters. Tap on the screen and drag the mini bubbles aim and lift it to shot. Take your time to aim and hit your desired bubble to make it pop.\nEasy to learn, only aim, match, and pop all the balls in this fun color-matching adventure. Use your puzzle-solving skills to clear levels and unlock new cities around the world. Travel with our heroine and discover amazing monuments, from Barcelona to the world. Clean the Jello and save the kidnapped birds.',0,'Puzzle',0,''),(258134,'Solar Struggle','Jul 09, 2022','Solar Struggle is an Ultimate Doom, limit-removing (Complevel 3) community project. Each map was given a name first and then participants were invited to make a level based of it.\n\nThe first 3 episodes are comparatively easy and short, and the 4th is ramping difficulty up quite a bit. The maps are balanced for pistol-start primarily.',0,'Shooter',0,'//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/co6tph.jpg'),(268167,'Train Simulator: Zhengxi Highspeed: Zhengzhou - Sanmenxia Route','','Experience exhilarating Chinese high-speed rail operations with the Zhengxi passenger line from SimTech Vision for Train simulator.',0,'Simulator',0,''),(268284,'Graviteam Tactics: Stalemate on Donets','','Izyum-Barvenkovo offensive operation of the Red Army was carried out from 17 to 27 July, 1943 by forces of South-Western Front in order to encircle and destroy the German group defending Donbass, as well to prevent the transfer of enemy troops to the Kursk region.',0,'Simulator, Strategy',0,''),(274149,'Crusades','Sep 04, 1999','Crusades: An Unholy War is a nine-level Ultimate Doom PWAD in episode four style made by Richard Wiles. It replaces maps E4M1-E4M9.',0,'Shooter',0,'//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/co7anz.jpg'),(274991,'Hi-5 DVD Game','2005','Hi-5 DVD Game is a DVD game released by Universal Studios Home Entertainment. This interactive DVD game comes with a set of coloured picture mats that are used to play ten games all presented by and featuring the original Hi-5 members. The winners of each game will be crowned a Hi-5 Action Hero by each of the Hi-5 members, from their respective games.',0,'',0,'//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/co7bdj.jpg'),(283003,'A.E.','2012','A.E. is a Space Invaders inspired game with a 3D view. In A.E. the earth is under attack by swarms of aliens who drop bomb after bomb and it\'s your job to defend planet Earth. You control a laser cannon that moves horizontally at the bottom of the screen. To earn point you should shoot all the alien forces before they shoot you! The game becomes more challenging when you progress in the game as the alien swarm splits up and attack you from several sides. This version is a homebrew version released in 2012',0,'',0,'//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/co7n6q.jpg'),(283004,'Porky\'s','TBD','Porky\'s was a prototype game designed for the ColecoVision in 1983. Revenge is sweet... and you\'re out to get it. You\'ve been \"had\" at Porky\'s, and you\'re out to blow it away. The action\'s hot and heavy and it\'s up to you to keep Pee Wee on his toes. If he succumbs to distraction, it\'s the pits! It\'s more fun than a greased pig... it\'s a blast!',0,'',0,'//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/co7n6z.jpg'),(283005,'Video Hustler','TBD','With an overhead view of the table, you play a billiards variant called \"Pocket Ball\" with just six object balls. Imprecise control over the aim and velocity of your shots. You\'ll discover the exicetiment of ball colliding. The silence and concentration of the billiard room, as well as the enthusiasm of the players will all be there for you.',0,'',0,'//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/co7n70.jpg'),(300977,'Disney\'s Peter Pan: Return to Neverland','Feb 22, 2002, Mar 28, 2002','Players take control of Peter Pan. He can fly with Pixie Dust if he has Tinker Bell, but if he runs out of Pixie Dust, Peter cannot fly. Enemies are in this game, but all can be defeated, except police officers. Enemies can be defeated by any attack, such as ground pounding, throwing his sword or fighting.',0,'Platform',0,'//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/co87by.jpg'),(303668,'Hidden Cats in Jigsaw Puzzle','Jun 29, 2024','The beautifully hand-drawn art of the Hidden Cats Series levels from Nukearts is now in a Jigsaw Puzzle game! Enjoy the free content from Paris City and get more from DLCs.',0,'Puzzle, Indie',0,'//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/co8duc.jpg'),(305010,'Street Fighter 6: Year 2 - Terry','Sep 24, 2024, Sep 24, 2024, Sep 24, 2024, Sep 24, ','Terry is the second DLC character in the Street Fighter 6: Year 2 Character/Ultimate Pass.\n\nTerry is planned for release in Autumn 2024 and will be the first guest character to appear in the main Street Fighter series followed by Mai planned for release in 2025.',0,'Fighting',0,''),(311462,'Paradise Up Above: Gold Label Edition','Jul 26, 2024','Paradise Up Above: Gold Label Edition comes with 18 total maps tak﻿ing place in beautiful tropical locales, majestic skybound islands, Heavenly hot-spots, and the sinister shadow of Hell that eternally follows Doomguy wherever he goes, even in his journey for a peaceful place to rest his weary hands.',0,'Shooter',0,'//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/co8luc.jpg'),(313700,'Idle Champions: Dr. Buzz Watson the Bee Familiar Pack','Jul 24, 2024, Jul 24, 2024','In this pack: Dr. Buzz Watson the Bee Familiar 2 Epic Potions of Speed 2 Epic Potions of Giant\'s Strength 2 Epic Potions of Clairvoyance',0,'Strategy, Adventure, Indie',0,''),(314668,'Cactiverse','Aug 24, 2024, Sep 09, 2024','The world of Cactiverse, where gardening meets dragon-fueled fun! Grow your cacti, unleash fireballs, and join a vibrant community on Discord. With weekly tournaments and hilarious gameplay, Cactiverse is your next obsession. Fun, challenging, and social—what more could you ask for?',0,'Simulator, Adventure, Arcade',0,'//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/co8q90.jpg'),(314733,'MadBreak','Jul 08, 2024','Dive into MadBreak, a captivating reimagining of the beloved \"Brick Breaker\" game. With each level, you\'ll face exhilarating challenges that push your skills to the limit. Can you master the unique twists and turns that MadBreak throws your way? Break through the ordinary and embrace the extraordinary. Test your reflexes, strategize your moves, and discover if you have what it takes to conquer MadBreak! Get ready for an adrenaline-fueled journey where every block shattered brings you closer to victory. Are you up for the challenge? Game SUPPORTs controller use!',0,'',0,'//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/co8qcq.jpg');
